name: Estimate
description: The data is an estimate only, not a direct measurement.

name: Good
description: The data has been examined and represents a reliable measurement.

name: Poor
description: The data should be considered as low quality and may have been rejected.

name: Suspect
description: The data should be treated as suspect.

name: Unchecked
description: The data has not been checked by any qualitative or quantitative method.
